(Unofficial) BONK Price Ticker
Unofficial community built $BONK price ticker extension for chrome

What does it do?
- Show current market price on the persistent ticker (default currency USD)
- Show prices in ETH/USD on click
- Show 24 hours % change, market cap and supply

This currently uses the uniswap Open API to retrieve price data and ticker changes
